<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201510/9d95e63a5cf3.jpg" width="936" height="557" title=" " alt=" " /> 
</p>
<p>
</p>
<h3>
	The Birth chandelier by Satoshi Itasaka
</h3>
<p>
	这盏枝形吊灯来自日本 h220430 设计事务所的 Satoshi Itasaka，灵感源于微弱光线下卵子受孕的瞬间。使用了几十个朝向中心的球形灯泡，相互之间以相同的距离排成一个球体，但光线并不明亮。每一个灯泡都吊上了一根松散的线，更加柔和，有复古的典雅。设计师希望以此能重新发现生命的美妙。感兴趣的话，<a href="http://www.h220430.jp/" target="_blank">可以关注他们其他的作品。</a> 
</p>
<p>
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201510/902921813465.jpg" width="1000" height="1000" title=" " alt=" " /><span> </span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201510/f58c31e7dbda.jpg" width="1000" height="667" title=" " alt=" " /><span> </span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201510/c7563702ac05.jpg" width="1000" height="667" title=" " alt=" " /><span> </span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201510/e8c0c8029ff5.jpg" width="1000" height="616" title=" " alt=" " /><span> </span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201510/4d77e6bca291.jpg" width="1000" height="680" title=" " alt=" " /> 
</p>
<p>
</p>
<h3>
	柯布西耶纪念小件 by Jaime Hayon&amp;卡西纳
</h3>
<p>
	这些木制的小物件是为了纪念柯布西耶逝世 50 周年，材料来自一颗种植在莱芒湖畔小别墅（villa “le lac”）庭院露台的泡桐树，因为无法治愈而送到了木工厂。意大利家具品牌卡西纳邀请设计师 Jaime Hayon 创作这组物品，包括鸟居、小鸟和秋千，它们可以用来存放明信片和书本，简单而富有诗意。
</p>
<p>
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201510/c4e441af6092.jpg" width="818" height="563" title=" " alt=" " /><span> </span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201510/c66ba2e5abb6.jpg" width="818" height="563" title=" " alt=" " /><span> </span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201510/3ad3081a0eff.jpg" width="818" height="563" title=" " alt=" " /><span> </span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201510/308d954bd39b.jpg" width="818" height="563" title=" " alt=" " /><span> </span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201510/5150fc5bc5fb.jpg" width="818" height="818" title=" " alt=" " /> 
</p>
<p>
</p>
<h3>
	工作室桌椅 by Schemata Architects
</h3>
<p>
	这套桌椅来自日本的建筑事务所 Schemata Architects，他们要为一个前身是教室的工作室定制。在四根木制的腿上用了白色的钢管做支撑，更加稳固且显得简洁有序。此外，木材和钢材，浅棕色和白色对比，让这套桌椅看起来很清爽。<a href="http://schemata.jp/w-workshop-furniture-for-studio-renova-ring/" target="_blank">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a> 
</p>
<p>
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201510/32ae5e29c89b.jpg" width="818" height="545" title=" " alt=" " /><span> </span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201510/48d0a305765e.jpg" width="818" height="546" title=" " alt=" " /><span> </span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201510/bd71cab08c65.jpg" width="818" height="545" title=" " alt=" " /><span> </span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201510/284e50f7d8c9.jpg" width="818" height="545" title=" " alt=" " /><span> </span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201510/1aa1aea9a4d6.jpg" width="818" height="546" title=" " alt=" " /> 
</p>
<p>
</p>
<h3>
	mini washer Machine by Kyumin Ha
</h3>
<p>
	这是韩国设计师 Kyumin Ha 设计的小型洗衣机，看上去近似一个榨汁机。上面的圆筒可以加入衣服，下面放水和洗衣液，然后就只需等待了。不过，体积太小也限制了它的功能，不能脱水排水，是一个半自动的洗衣机，因而它更加适合个人清理小型衣物，作为大型洗衣机的附属。
</p>
<p>
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201510/1225be6c3d2e.jpg" width="1050" height="1031" title=" " alt=" " /><span> </span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201510/b53ed3a37033.jpg" width="1050" height="311" title=" " alt=" " /><img src="/uploads/image/201510/d1eae5dba5e4.jpg" width="1050" height="728" title=" " alt=" " /> 
</p>
<p>
</p>
<p>
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201510/6c9fae7800da.jpg" width="1050" height="743" title=" " alt=" " /><span> </span> 
</p>
<p>
	<span> </span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201510/386e075870d2.jpg" width="1050" height="1050" title=" " alt=" " /> 
</p>
<p>
</p>
<p>
</p>
<p>
</p>
<h3>
	Inner City Bikes by &nbsp;Joey Ruiter
</h3>
<p>
	这辆小型自行车 BIG20 来自 Joey Ruiter，它带有一个 1×10 的传动系统，小型的车轮和框架让它几乎是自行车里的极简设计，但也拥有一个直接利落的现代感。因为重量很轻，非常容易携带，骑着它在拥挤的街上穿梭能很好地避开人群并找到停靠的位置。&nbsp;
</p>
<p>
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201510/42879620802d.jpg" width="900" height="600" title=" " alt=" " /><span> </span> 
</p>
<p>
</p>
<p>
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201510/f784538e84c7.jpg" width="900" height="600" title=" " alt=" " /><span> </span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201510/ac6e520aefd6.jpg" width="900" height="600" title=" " alt=" " /><span> </span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201510/3628bb39100f.jpg" width="600" height="900" title=" " alt=" " /><span> </span> 
</p>
